  "body": "### Component\n\nCast, Anvil\n\n### Have you ensured that all of these are up to date?\n\n- [X] Foundry\n- [ ] Foundryup\n\n### What version of Foundry are you on?\n\nforge 0.2.0 (152e200 2022-09-13T00:05:42.069519Z)\n\n### What command(s) is the bug in?\n\ncast call\n\n### Operating System\n\nmacOS (Apple Silicon)\n\n### Describe the bug\n\nHi! I'm running:\r\n```\r\nanvil --fork-url https://aurora-mainnet.infura.io/v3/3ea24ab163f04f4893a91af359d24258\r\n```\r\nAnd trying to get the [USDT (0xdAC17F958D2ee523a2206206994597C13D831ec7)](https://etherscan.io/address/0xdac17f958d2ee523a2206206994597c13d831ec7) `balanceOf` `0xf39fd6e51aad88f6f4ce6ab8827279cfffb92266` (first anvil-generated account) using the following `cast` command:\r\n```\r\ncast call 0xdAC17F958D2ee523a2206206994597C13D831ec7 --from 0xf39fd6e51aad88f6f4ce6ab8827279cfffb92266 \"balanceOf(address account) external view returns (uint256)\" 0xf39fd6e51aad88f6f4ce6ab8827279cfffb92266\r\n```\r\n\r\nThe error is:\r\n```\r\nError:\r\n(code: -32603, message: EVM error OutOfGas, data: None)\r\n```",
