    "body": "thanks for this\r\n\r\nturns out aurora's gas limit is always `0` in the `eth_getBlockByNumber` response, I guess since it's basically unlimited: https://doc.aurora.dev/compat/evm/#gaslimit\r\n\r\nthis resulted in anvil setting `0` for the block gas limit, basically always ensuring OutOfgas\r\n\r\nI guess the right fix here would be to not set the gas limit of it's 0\r\n\r\n\r\n",
